{"tid":216498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍皇帝「墨寶」遭白油掩蓋","createTime":"2017-04-25T08:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T09:06:26.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e586843ec5fbda2f1daebfdfb04decc2b5e964b8","tid":216498,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"「九龍皇帝」曾灶財遺下的「墨寶」曾經遍佈港九，甚至曾於2003年威尼斯雙年展展出，但他的作品一直不被政府承認為藝術品，2007曾灶財去世後政府更逐步消滅他的遺作，4月24日傳媒人陳雲海在Facebook發文，揭發政府近日派員用白油掩蓋觀塘一電箱，將曾灶財遺留多年的作品徹底破壞，令香港永久失去一個文化遺產及景點，當有網民貼出電箱原貌相片時，雲海更慨嘆留言：「無晒！！！！」<br />\n<br />\n事發地點發生於觀塘道近啟德大廈的一個電箱，根據市民圖文描述，本來該電箱有曾灶財的字迹，寫上「新中國皇」、「香港政府曾灶財」等字樣，但根據最近拍下的照片，該電箱已完全塗上白油，「墨寶」已無法修復。"},{"pid":"7a92c2ff65e2f940ed276ba073b844cb93d823dd","tid":216498,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/18058059_1491959024179560_8729005133601840320_n.jpg?oh=5ecbfd3f4bc30117430433f87328cada&amp;oe=59982159\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F18058059_1491959024179560_8729005133601840320_n.jpg%3Foh%3D5ecbfd3f4bc30117430433f87328cada%26oe%3D59982159&h=eef3f17f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca4f6ce3e9aa63254aa5e7bfbd81e4290d64b13","tid":216498,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"政府你乜料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又外判商呀?"},{"pid":"5f2f844013836af1e4bd8f921de0872ccbe89311","tid":216498,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12b1c2e28922643027e